About Me
docs.text: Hi, I'm Sunil Sharma, a passionate Python Developer and Data Scientist. I specialize in creating innovative solutions and sharing my knowledge through blogs. With a strong background in data analysis and machine learning, I strive to turn data into actionable insights.

docs.title: Experience
docs.text: I have worked on various projects involving data analysis, machine learning, and web development. My goal is to leverage my skills to solve real-world problems and contribute to the tech community.
